Package: BrandTargetArea
Title: Brand Target Area Visualization App
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bayer", "Crop Science", , email = "example@bayer.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An interactive Shiny application for visualizing brand target 
    areas and P4 breeding locations across the United States. Displays choropleth 
    maps of acreage by county and breeding site locations with filtering capabilities.
